name: Bedroom
content: You wake up in your bedroom.  [[Go to the kitchen]]  [[Go to the bathroom]]

name: Go to the kitchen
content: You make breakfast. It's very warm and nice.  [[Go to the bathroom]] [[Go to bed]]

name: Go to the bathroom
content: You brush your teeth. You have your favorite flavor of toothpaste.  [[Go to the CMC]]

name: Go to bed
content: Whelp, it's been a good morning. Time to go back to sleep I guess.
